indicator_value: The Grievance Policy has been shared with all employees, along with the list of committee members and guidelines for filing grievances.
The Grievance Policy has been shared with all employees, along with the list of committee members and guidelines for filing grievances.

The workers of the Company may report their grievances / complaints to their respective Head of Departments / immediate superior which is escalated to the HR department of the Company in case of non satisfactory resolution. Policy: https://www.sanghicement.com/wp content/uploads/Employee-Grievance-Management-Policy.pdf
